Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}臉色也比剛才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}頭昏了吧 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次和你這樣見面 還是在墓地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當時被你弄得好慘 都忘不掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他不記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真會給我找麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 你都答應交易了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都受到了一樣強烈的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是永生的詛咒 你是必死的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以把你的左手給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是想要我的手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在看來 那是最派得上用場的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為代價 我也把我的一部分給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣你就有不會死的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我無法信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還有其他選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只要給你手臂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得先確認有沒有排斥反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 接下來輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼 還是很害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣說不定就能解除你的詛咒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心 你不會變成別的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我果然討厭你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 移植完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事啦 只是流點血不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有排斥反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你眼裡的世界 全都閃耀著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是世上獨一無二 能看到同樣事物的一對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等詛咒融入你的身體 再取下這隻手臂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心 你昏睡的時候就會全部結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}借用一下留在你眼睛上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說過吧 我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 很懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你回來啦 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你看家 沒什麼可怕的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 有史輝陪我 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好史輝像爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是爸爸和弟弟消失前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史輝是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會換尿布啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的耶 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 媽媽 我也要幫忙做晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎 你要幫忙做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.63,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼都能幫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊 以前還有個笑得那麼開心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你回來啦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我全身濕透了 你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你回來啦 夕輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.22,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 我走不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來我是像爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}工作很辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟最近晚班增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 要是我也能工作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智花不是在照顧家裡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且智世有著跟你一樣麻煩的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有你陪著她 我比較放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 夕輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}體質…原來媽媽也跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他為了不讓我醒來 讓我進入了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卡達…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 你不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是那東西分離出的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那東西結合了很多不一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但哪一個才是真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己究竟是什麼東西 卻已經不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼給我看這麼久遠的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是想讓你難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然它會傷害到你 但也會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它也是你能和我這樣的東西對話的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是別碰我的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除非你下定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}決心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事 我來哄他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 我就出去一下 等我回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之後爸爸就再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再也沒回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的記憶只到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以這扇門是打不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夕輝？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊 就是這一天起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼又是你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近總是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從羽鳥太太來了之後開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要我幫你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明是媽媽說了不能害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救我 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 大半夜的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要保護她 保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直保護她們的男人最近不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真可憐 是耐心耗盡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被拋棄的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被拋棄的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既可憐又可口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 我必須保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一個人也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是沒有那孩子 我就能更輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 要是沒有那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒生過你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要是 沒生過你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽…媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷人 真傷人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太傷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是沒生下你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你這樣的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是死了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去死 去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去死 去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你為什麼沒下殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是住在我心裡的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是被媽媽掐過脖子的我 創造出的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好和奈威說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡 賽門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛麗絲他們 林德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妖精之國的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 西魯基 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我慶幸自己遇上了這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然在見到你之前 我肯定就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:20.22,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}両手塞いでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:28.90,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}たくさんの思い出に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:44.27,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}さようならとキスを送ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.43,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}窓の外の雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.99,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}眺めてるだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:06.25,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}もうおしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.38,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}前に進めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:19.87,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}わたしだけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:28.45,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}どこまでも続く空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.32,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}tick-tock, tick-tock
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:35.52,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}誰にも止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:42.80,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}ひとつずつ選んでゆく未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:50.76,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}辿りつけたら　何が見えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:20:02.04,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}聞いたことのないハーモニーを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:12.02,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}誰と歌おう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:20.22,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}兩手中塞滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:28.90,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}數不清的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:44.27,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}輕輕一吻 向它們告別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.43,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}窗外白雪紛紛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.99,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}別開眺望的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:06.25,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}推開房間的門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.38,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}向天地邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:19.87,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}續寫屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:28.45,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}追逐那無垠的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.32,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}滴滴答答 滴滴答答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:35.52,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}時光的河流奔騰不息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:42.80,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}沿著一個個目標前行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:50.76,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}最終會找到怎樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:20:02.04,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那陌生的溫婉和聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:12.02,IN-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}誰又會與你歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原諒我 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 你為我付出很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直付出 一直付出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而到了最後還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前很喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有過很多愉快的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自從那天起 我卻再也想不起那些了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但也是媽媽 讓我遇上了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個我比自己還看重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還以為是個強悍的人 其實是很麻煩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 那天鬆開了你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我仍然不會忘記你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我會離開你 向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下定決心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是賦予永生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是他背負上的詛咒與祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是約瑟夫…卡達菲爾斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們將我種在你身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你正要接受我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以如果你想活下去 我會成為你的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即便要和侵蝕你 保護你的野獸永遠互相撕咬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的願望是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}代價是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為聽起來對我太有利了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有個聽過無數遍的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有辦法實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}適應度似乎已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是醜陋 和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也學學你的手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道能否幫你實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我可以傾聽 然後想想辦法付諸行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾百年 幾千年以來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們一直在那樣呼喊
